    <h1 class='text-4xl'>
      Swiset, building a design system with an approach to identity, usability
      and accessibility
    </h1>
    <Paragraph title='Introduction'>
      This was one of the most interesting projects for me, because apart from
      learning a lot about the design systems, it was also a very enriching
      experience in the sense of teamwork. In this case study I will share with
      you how we approached and built a design system.
    </Paragraph>

