    <Paragraph title='ðŸªªâ€ Visual Identity'>
      The visual identity is extremely important when building a coherent design
      system, because it is this aspect that gives us the context. Swiset is a
      modern, institutional Fintech and wants to transmit seriousness and
      accessibility in its products, so these principles will guide us when
      designing.
    </Paragraph>

