    <Paragraph title='Radius & Shadow'>
      With these elements we finish the basis of our design system, the corner
      radius is essential to create components such as modals, pop ups,
      information blocks, buttons among many others, this element will give a
      better look and differentiate it from the background. The shadow is an
      equally important element, and helps us to create depth and
      differentiation between the element we want to show and the background.
    </Paragraph>

